name: The Sakura Has You
description:
Title: The Sakura Has You
Location: Salem, Oregon
Year Taken: 2019
About this photo:  Tara had joined me in my studio for a boudoir photo session highlighting her cosplays based on the Japanese anime character Sakura. Of the many epic photographs we shot, this one, a feature of her intense eyes, brought out a digital creation that is a good callback to the popular film: ‘The Matrix.’ My finished piece was definitely inspired.
